      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Grown from magical trees shaped by song, Uzodian starships often include unique components that other societies have attempted to replicate. Even the most successful facsimiles mimic only the basic functions, without capturing the underlying intelligence.</p><h2>Uzodian Starship Weapons</h2><p>Sonic weapons barely project a whisper in the vacuum of space. Undeterred, Xibian engineers developed dual-purpose cannons that create a dense line of particles and then channel a sonic surge along that line to shatter anything at the other end.</p>"
